    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u on the environment thing but i've been reading some old papers and certain modern studies that argue the environmental stuff doesn't explain the whole gap. like, if you look at the heritability scales, some researchers claim there's a much stronger biological component than most people admit. can u dig into the specific arguments that suggest these differences are actually innate/genetic?",
